text: Mohammad Ami-Tehrani (, 20 September 1935 - 15 March 2020) was an Iranian middleweight weightlifter. He won bronze medals at the 1962 World Championships and 1966 Asian Games and placed sixth at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Olympians for Iran Category:Iranian weightlifters
